{
  "stem": "7455.7",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They gave me-- now-- [? no, ?] [? now what ?] am I saying?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we have to present those documents, and you have to-- they told me-- I-- I went because I already had-- was registered.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They told me I have to provide a photograph.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took those documents that I had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in few days, when I have a photo to bring it, where they going to put it on, on that new document.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I waited anxiously.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The document came, my Kennkarte.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I felt I have sort of a-- my lifeline is extended.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And with those documents, somehow, I felt I'm convincing the boys.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in meantime, the front kept coming closer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Winer was thinking of leaving town because they're going to evacuate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We already knew that so many, so many kilometer, the Germans were retreating.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Winer is to go-- go on the German side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she sold the cow, and she's liquidating-- packing up everything, putting in the attic there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And now I won't have any employment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Popel has to leave, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She's evacuating.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she is-- she was only crying that she has her little dog is going to suffer when they have a hardships and so.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We came-- I came to say goodbye to her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she's now sending Hania, the girl, away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Hania, I thought she has family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She didn't have anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So where is Hania going to go?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she cannot stay in her apartment because the Germans were confiscating these apartments, and the front line is coming.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Winer said, how about you looking for a little place, apartment-- you shack up with Hania?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said, you could take some parts of the furniture.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So Hania went, was the spoke girl.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
